                                                                                                      data.txtpackage files;

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                                                                                       data.txtpackage files;

                                                                                                                                                                               import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.util.List;

                                                                                                                                                                               public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                                                                                   public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                                                                                       Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                                                                                       List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                                                                                       System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                                                                                       Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                                                                                   }
                                                                                                                                                                                package files;

                                                                 import java.io.IOException;
                                                                 import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                 import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                 import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                 import java.util.List;

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 import java.io.IOException;

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {

                                                                     }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                                                                                                                               import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                                                                                               import java.util.List;

                                                                                                                                                                               public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                                                                                   public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                                                                                       Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                                                                                       List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                                                                                       System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                                                                                       Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                                                                                   }
                                                                                                                                                                               }

                                                                 import java.util.List;

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {

                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                                                                                                                                       List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Files;

                                                                                                                                                                               import java.nio.file.Paths;

                                                                                                                                                                               public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                                                                                   public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                                                                                       Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                                                                                       List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                                                                                       System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                                                                                       Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                                                                                   }
                                                                                                                                                                               }

                                                                 import java.util.List;

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                                                                                                                               public class FileReadExcercise {

                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                                                                                                                               public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                                                                                   public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                                                                                       Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                                                                                       List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                                                                                       System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                                                                                       Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                                                                                   }

                                                                 import java.util.List;

                                                                 public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                     public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                         Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

                                                                         List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                         System.out.println(lines);
                                                                         Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                     }
                                                                 }

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                      data.txtpackage files;

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                      data.txtpackage files;

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }

                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);

                                                                                                                  }

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }

        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }

    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }

    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

                                                                                                      data.txtpackage files;

                                                                                                              import java.io.IOException;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Files;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Path;
                                                                                                              import java.nio.file.Paths;
                                                                                                              import java.util.List;

                                                                                                              public class FileReadExcercise {
                                                                                                                  public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
                                                                                                                      Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
                                                                                                                      List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
                                                                                                                      System.out.println(lines);
                                                                                                                      Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
                                                                                                                  }
                                                                                                              }
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }

        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

    }
}
package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

package files;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

import java.nio.file.Path;
import java.nio.file.Paths;
import java.util.List;

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}

public class FileReadExcercise {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Path pathFileToRead = Paths.get("D:\\Google Drive\\programming\\notes\\ambil.txt");
        List<String> lines = Files.readAllLines(pathFileToRead);
        System.out.println(lines);
        Files.lines(pathFileToRead).map(String::toLowerCase).filter(str -> str.contains("lihat")).forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
